# 📊 Amazon Sales Data Analysis & Forecasting

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing e-commerce sales data and predicting future sales trends using advanced data analytics and machine learning techniques.

---

## 📁 Dataset

* 100,000+ records of Amazon-style sales data
* Features include product details, pricing, location, and order dates

---

## 🧹 Data Cleaning

* Handled missing values and duplicates
* Standardized column names
* Converted date formats
* Removed outliers for accurate forecasting

---

## 📊 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

* Identified top-selling products and categories
* Analyzed monthly and yearly sales trends
* Evaluated regional performance

---

## 🔮 Forecasting Models

* ARIMA (Time Series Forecasting)
* Prophet (Advanced Forecasting with Seasonality)

---

## 🤖 Machine Learning

* Built regression model to predict sales
* Evaluated model performance using R² score

---

## 📊 Dashboard

* Developed Power BI dashboard with:

  * KPI metrics
  * Sales trends
  * Product insights
  * Forecast visualization

---

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies

* Python (Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn)
* Machine Learning (Scikit-learn)
* Forecasting (ARIMA, Prophet)
* Power BI

---

## 📈 Key Insights

* Identified peak sales periods
* Found high-performing products and regions
* Predicted future sales trends for business planning

---

## 📌 Conclusion

This project demonstrates end-to-end data analysis, forecasting, and dashboard creation, providing valuable business insights.

